               <p>The Prosecutor depos'd, That the Cloth hung out at her Window for Show, and she being gone up Stairs, her Neighbour call'd to her, asking her, if she would stay there, and let her Shop be Robb'd? That she came down, but they had got the Cloth, and ran away with it, but were afterwards taken; and one of them confess'd that it had been Sold in Rag-Fair.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17300704-44-person280">
