                  </persName>
             depos'd, That she living over-against the Prosecutor, saw the Prisoner lurking about her Window, and suspecting them, ask'd them, what they had to do at her Window? That they gave her saucy Language, and she saw Wheeler take the Cloth, and Collins standing at a little Distance from him, and she going towards them, they ran away, she was positive to the Prisoners; the Fact being plainly prov'd, the Jury found them <rs id="t17300704-44-verdict209" type="verdictDescription">
